ss="_ _b"></span>人生确实是一场梦，<span class="_ _b"></span>这一点，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y1d6 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">你们若详细学过《醒与梦的辩论》<span class="_ _8"></span>，就会有特别深的体会。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y14 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">以前我刚到佛学院不久时，<span class="_ _5"></span>上师如意宝就传过<span class="_ _4"></span>《醒与梦</div><div class="t m0 x9 h7 y1d7 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">                                        <span class="_ _2"></span>               <span class="_ _4"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x9 he y16e ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8</div><div class="t m0 x22 hf y16f ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">  <span class="ffb">堪布根据现代人的特点，<span class="_ _4"></span>深入浅出地讲过<span class="_ _4"></span>《入菩萨行论》<span class="_ _12"></span>，<span class="_ _4"></span>其全套视频、<span class="_ _4"></span>音频、</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 hf y170 ffb fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">讲记，现收录于“智悲佛网”<span class="_ _12"></span>。<span class="ff6"> </span></div><div class="t m0 x9 he y17 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9</div><div class="t m0 x22 hf y18 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">  <span class="ffb">《醒与梦的辩论》<span class="_ _12"></span>，现收录于《显密宝库<span class="_ _10"> </span><span class="ff6">05</span>—窍诀宝藏海》<span class="_ _23"></span>。<span class="ff6"> </span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
